snippet.title: Psychic readings by Andre !
snippet.description:
Hi my name is Andre and I have been doing readings for about ten years. I have taught classes such as:
flame reading
meditation
soul reading
aura reading and many more...
I'm also knowledgeable in many healing arts.
I have done many one on one readings and group readings. 
I am offering half hour readings for $40 on Skype or in person.
